        "title": "How do I clear the selection in a ButtonGroup such that no elements of the associated set of abstract buttons are selected?",
        "body": "<p>I have created 5 radioButton group. I want user clear all group in one click.\ni use java 1.5.<\/p>\n\n<p><strong>Does any one know how to do it?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n<pre><code>public void actionCommandCLEAR() {\n        timeGroup.setSelected(timeGroup.getSelection(),false);\n        dateGroup.setSelected(dateGroup.getSelection(),false);\n        docGroup.setSelected(docGroup.getSelection(),false);\n        socGroup.setSelected(socGroup.getSelection(),false);\n\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
        "question_id": 13033050,
        "tags": [
            "java",
            "swing",
            "jradiobutton",
            "buttongroup"
        ],
        "score": 1,
        "closed_reason": "exact duplicate",
        "is_answered": true,
        "view_count": 11254,
        "last_edit_date": 1351070885
    },
    "question_comments": [],
    "answers": [
        {
            "owner": {
                "user_type": "does_not_exist",
                "display_name": "user1766873"
            },
            "content_license": "CC BY-SA 3.0",
            "score": 3,
            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1351004760,
            "creation_date": 1351004007,
            "body": "<pre><code>timeGroup.clearSelection();\ndateGroup.clearSelection();\ndocGroup.clearSelection();\nsocGroup.clearSelection();\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>for java 1.5 we need to code clearSelection ourselves:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>void cleartSelection(ButtonGroup bg) {\n Enumeration&lt;AbstractButton&gt; e =bg.getElements(); \n    while(e.hasMoreElements()) {\n        AbstractButton b = e.nextElement();\n        b.setSelected(false);\n    }\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>and <\/p>\n\n<pre><code>clearSelection(timeGroup);\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
            "answer_id": 13033257,
            "question_id": 13033050,
            "last_edit_date": 1351004760
        },
        {
            "owner": {
                "profile_image": "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/65b08e060a0e964824f57522f79366ac?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG&f=y&so-version=2",
